{"type": "article", "id": 18496, "title": "Kylie Jenner 唇膏", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-04T07:40:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000404KgXLJWjy5bz3xte4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这套化妆品系列的包装借用了 Kylie Jenner 的红唇，上面滴了一半对应颜色的奶油状的液体，有点“秀色可餐”。三支唇膏的色调偏暗，配合着包装也做了一个暗处理，一个大红唇放在白纸中间，下面用黑体字标上 Kylie ，像一幅海报，有点 90 年代的感觉。盒子里的唇膏瓶保留了液体滴下来的状态，可以联想到血液或者油漆等涂鸦艺术，很有个性。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000401gfYMHcNQ9oJIhpDV.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000402vhOzQHIfY3mt9u7j.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000402mNhRj4lIY1QWMkLw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000403EHq2476OuXdijs9z.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}